node.text:
Nourishing and Soothing bowls of Tang Shui from @thechinesepotion
.
Generous ingredients filled in each container available at $6.00 each. Each container is able to fill up 2 full bowls as shown in the picture. This is really worth it!
.
Total 4 options in the menu
1️⃣ Snow Fungus with Pear
2️⃣ Peach Gum with Apple & Osmanthus
3️⃣ Snow Lotus Seed with Papaya
4️⃣ Gum Tragacanth with Dried Longan and Dried Lily Bulb
.
To order, WhatsApp them at 9763 5766. 2 days advance order is required
.
